## NotchedOutline

### Markup

```html
<m-textfield
  outlined
  id="outlined">
  <m-floating-label for="outlined">Outlined</m-floating-label>
  <m-notched-outline />
</m-textfield>
```

### Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| notched | Boolean | false | open notch outline |
